=Sanlun zong 三論宗=
"three-treatise school", school of buddhism

==Persons==
* [[吉藏]] (549-623)
* [[印順]] (1906-2005)

==Works==
* Nāgārjuna's Mūlamadhyamakakārikā, "Fundamental Verses on the Middle Way", 中論, T. 1564
* Nāgārjuna's Dvādaśanikāyaśāstra, "Treatise on the Twelve Gates", 十二門論, T. 1568
* Āryadeva's Śatakaśāstra, "Hundred-Verse Treatise", 百論, T. 1569
